// Windows application icon for bumpy_port. Explorer/taskbar use the icon group
// with the lowest resource id, so this claims id 1. bumpy.ico is a multi-size
// (16..256) pixel-art render of the Bumpy hero sprite, built by
// tools/re/build_icon.py from a BUMSPJEU frame -- see that script's header.
1 ICON "bumpy.ico"
